# REST Client file Availability

### Get all buses
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/fleet/availability/buses
Accept: application/json

### Get bus by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/fleet/availability/buses/1
Accept: application/json

### Get all seats
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/fleet/availability/seats
Accept: application/json

### Get seat by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/fleet/availability/seats/1
Accept: application/json

### Get all seat types
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/fleet/availability/seat-types
Accept: application/json

### Get seat type by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/fleet/availability/seat-types/1
Accept: application/json

### Search buses
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/fleet/availability/buses/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plateNumber": "ABC",
  "totalCapacity": null,
  "isActive": null
}

### Search seats
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/fleet/availability/seats/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "letter": null,
  "number": null
}

### Search seat types
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/fleet/availability/seat-types/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Premium",
  "upcharge": null
}
